{
  "name": "xml-xlsx-lite",

  "version": "1.7.4",
  "description": "🚀 Lightweight Excel XLSX generator with full Excel features: dynamic pivot tables, charts, styles, and Chinese support. Fast, TypeScript-friendly Excel file creation library. | 輕量級 Excel XLSX 生成器，支援樞紐分析表、圖表、樣式，完整繁體中文支援。",
  "main": "dist/index.js",
  "types": "dist/index.d.ts",
  "module": "dist/index.esm.js",
  "exports": {
    ".": {
      "types": "./dist/index.d.ts",
      "import": "./dist/index.esm.js",
      "require": "./dist/index.js"
    }
  },
  "files": [
    "dist",
